<L>__{interior zabar's cashier area continuous}
<A>__{kathleen, now wearing dark glasses but looking not at all disguised, looks around and spots a short line and makes a beeline for it. at that moment, joe comes from the appetizing department and gets on the line she was heading for. panicked, kathleen retreats onto another line and stands with her back to him.}
